## üî• Action Required
```dataview
TASK
FROM "Daily Notes"
WHERE !completed AND !contains(text, "#waiting")
SORT
  contains(text, "#P1") desc,
  contains(text, "#P2") desc,
  contains(text, "#P3") desc,
  file.day desc

```


## ‚è≥ Waiting on others

```dataview
TASK
FROM "Daily Notes"
WHERE !completed AND contains(text, "#waiting")
SORT file.day desc

```


## Aging Action Items - P1 over 3 days

```dataview
TASK
FROM "Daily Notes"
WHERE !completed
  AND contains(text, "#p1")
  AND file.day <= date(today) - dur(3 days)
SORT file.day asc

```

## üîÅ Carryover Radar
```dataview
TASK
FROM "Daily Notes"
WHERE !completed AND file.day <= date(today) - dur(7 days)
SORT file.day asc
```
